6.narrative: find countries with more players who won the ballon d'Or
6.query: SELECT ?country ?name count(*) AS ?won WHERE { ?people wdt:P27 ?country; wdt:P106 wd:Q937857; wdt:P166 wd:Q166177. ?country sc:name ?name } GROUP BY ?country ?name HAVING (count(*) > 1) ORDER BY DESC (?won)

7.narrative: find clubs with more players who won the ballon d'Or
7.query: SELECT ?team ?name count(*) AS ?won WHERE { ?player wdt:P106 wd:Q937857; wdt:P54 ?team ; wdt:P106 wd:Q937857; wdt:P166 wd:Q166177. ?team sc:name ?name } GROUP BY ?team ?name HAVING (count(*) > 1) ORDER BY DESC (?won) LIMIT 5
